item.title: Nathan Lane & Ernie Sabella & Jason Weaver & Joseph Williams - Hakuna Matata - Key of C - Fredonia Ukulele Club
item.description: Play along video for the song Hakuna Matata by Nathan Lane & Ernie Sabella & Jason Weaver & Joseph Williams from the channel Fredonia Ukulele Club. Chords used in the song: Am, B♭, C, D, E♭, F, G, G7.
